CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 9, 1957, pg. 12, reads: "Fifth Avenue Choir - The Senior Red Circle MIssionary Society of Macedonia Baptist Church presented the choir from Fifth Avenue High School in a musical program at the church, under the direction of Miss Durant. Officers of the circle are Miss Richards, sponsor; Joan Matthews, president, and Arlene Thompson, secretary. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Fifth Avenue High School choir singing with woman playing piano, in Macedonia Baptist Church
